        <p>
            Mantis Estimation™ is a system for quickly estimating damage in Pokémon battles without using a damage calculator. 
            It provides two key values: <strong>power</strong> (how powerful an attack is, typically 1-8, calculated as <code>(Attack Stat × Base Power × 0.714 × STAB) ÷ 10,000</code>) 
            and <strong>bulk</strong> (how well a Pokémon can withstand attacks, typically 3-12, calculated as <code>(HP × Def/SpD) ÷ 10,000</code>). 
            Simply divide power by bulk to estimate damage percentage. For example, a power 4.2 move against bulk 11.1 = ~38% damage.
